00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:56,880
 tako posutruženo.

515
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,180
 Ja imam uspodne i padove.

516
00:24:58,180 --> 00:24:59,680
 Ja plaćem i imam ono

517
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,020
