00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:07,680
 kao do Aruše do Dare Salama

521
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:09,400
 i to je taj jedini ispravni put.

522
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:11,840
 Nema latica, nema ništa.

523
00:25:11,840 --> 00:25:13,600
 Onako težake.

524
00:25:13,600 --> 00:25:15,500
 Ali kad dođeš na kraj tog puta

525
00:25:15,500 --> 00:25:16,940
 čuda te čekaju.

526
00:25:16,940 --> 00:25:18,060
 I onda na nju ubiti

527
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:19,560
 nam je Afrika inspiracija

528
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:21,360
 da se vratimo na jedne

529
00:25:21,360 --> 00:25:22,720
 tehničke postavke.

530
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:23,420
 Pa da.

