551
00:25:49,740 --> 00:25:51,760
 Tako da djeca su uvijek iskrene

552
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:52,220
 i to oni,

553
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:53,780
 mislim,

554
00:25:53,780 --> 00:25:54,580
 otiću,

555
00:25:54,580 --> 00:25:55,960
 svaki čovjek je treba otići

556
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:58,060
 na to u edukaciju u Afriku.

557
00:25:58,060 --> 00:25:58,380
 I to,

558
00:25:58,380 --> 00:25:59,000
 mislim,

559
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:00,120
 meni se to uvuko,

560
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:00,900
 taj život,

561
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:02,880
 taj stil,

562
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:03,440
 način,

563
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,040
 ta ulica,

564
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:04,820
 kad ste vi na ulici,

565
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:06,440
 kad ste među tim ljudima,

566
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:07,760
 meni se to uvuklo u krvi.

567
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:08,640
 jednostavno onaka,

568
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:10,060
 kad dođem tamo,

569
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:10,340
 onako,

570
00:26:10,340 --> 00:26:11,320
 ili moguće da sam,

571
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:11,640
 ono,

572
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:12,240
 nemam hrane,

573
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,180
 nekad nemaš vode,

574
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:14,320
 ne možeš ješta hoćeš,

575
00:26:14,320 --> 00:26:14,740
 bosi,

576
00:26:14,740 --> 00:26:15,400
 prašina,

577
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,120
 bolesti,

578
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:17,520
 ono,

579
00:26:17,520 --> 00:26:19,360
 kak je moguće da si toliko sretan?

580
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:19,760
 Ono,

581
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:21,240
 zato što je ta energija

582
