00:26:25,060 --> 00:26:26,260
 U Africi svi jure.

587
00:26:26,260 --> 00:26:27,840
 Uvijek je puno ljudi,

588
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:28,860
 stalno neko negdje ide,

589
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:29,420
 vamo tamo,

590
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:30,480
 ali ne jure za novcem,

591
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:31,600
 to je ono specifično.

592
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:34,080
 I to je onako,

593
00:26:34,080 --> 00:26:37,740
 i ne mogu vjerao da te doživljavaju ljudi na ulici.

594
00:26:37,740 --> 00:26:38,320
 Tamo je ono,

595
00:26:38,320 --> 00:26:38,860
 ne znam koliko,

596
00:26:38,860 --> 00:26:40,740
 8 milijuna sam ono niko dare salam.

597
00:26:40,740 --> 00:26:41,000
 Ono,

598
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:41,600
 svi ono,

599
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,760
 na ulici te dožive,

600
00:26:42,760 --> 00:26:43,500
 pozdrave,

601
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:45,560
 osmijek ti dadu.

602
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:46,100
 Ono,

603
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:47,140
 kad ste vidjeli zadnji put

604
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:48,320
 da vam je neko darovao osmijek.

605
00:26:48,320 --> 00:26:49,740
 Kad sam ja sreo u kafiću

606
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:50,780
 da neko se obrati meni,

607
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:51,380
 to je ono,

608
00:26:51,380 --> 00:26:52,360
 užas.

609
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:53,600
 Ili pomoć na ulici.

610
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:53,720
 Od konobara,

611
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:54,800
 ili od konobara,

612
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:56,720
 ili znam da svi rade te teške posle,

613
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:58,720
 ne očekujem da sad tamo pjevam i pjesme,

